---
import ArticleLayout from '../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="Vehicle Dynamics Consultancy | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="VEHICLE DYNAMICS CONSULTANCY"
  subheading="Pursue your competition."
  image="/images/pages/vehicle-dynamics-hero.jpg"
  imagePosition="center 50%"
  description="Vehicle dynamics consultancy covering K&C analysis, suspension testing, damper tuning, lap time simulation and component design — tangible performance outcomes."
>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We are specialists in vehicle dynamics, where depth of knowledge and methodical approach produces tangible performance outcomes. Constant research and development in this discipline enables us to shine in a wide range of applications, from ride comfort and NVH for the road to closing down on your competitors at the track.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">At its heart, vehicle dynamics is simply the manipulation of forces and moments. With our expertise we will ensure your project objectives are met and keep you ahead of competition.</p>

  <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">By implementing a tyre-centric approach together with an understanding of the importance of subjective, human considerations to augment data driven engineering, we demonstrate our success in tailoring this methodology to suit clients requirements and will offer you the following:</p>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Test &amp; Development</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>Vehicle Testing and Test Support
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Lab based</li>
        <li>Track based</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Vertical Dynamics Optimisation
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Setup rig testing</li>
        <li>Damper tuning</li>
        <li>Spring rate specification</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Kinematics &amp; Compliance (K&amp;C) Analysis
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>K&amp;C mapping</li>
        <li>K&amp;C development</li>
        <li>Static geometry optimisation</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>CoG &amp; Moment of Inertia Testing</li>
    <li>Data Analysis
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Instrumentation</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Ride &amp; Performance Evaluations
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Subjective &amp; Objective</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>General Chassis Optimisation</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Design</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>Component Design
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Control arms</li>
        <li>Uprights</li>
        <li>Anti-roll bars</li>
        <li>Mode decoupling systems</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Component Specification</li>
    <li>Reverse Engineering</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Simulation</h2>
  <ul class="wd-list mb-10 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li>Vehicle Dynamics Simulation
      <ul class="wd-list mt-2 ml-2 space-y-1 list-none">
        <li>Lap time optimisation</li>
        <li>Simulation lap testing</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Multibody Dynamics Analysis</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">We look forward to discussing your requirements and developing a solution for your project.</p>

  <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors">Get in Touch →</a>

</ArticleLayout>
